China to Curb Three Gorges Dam Environmntal Impact, Xinhua News Reports

-- B y   B l o o m b e r g   N e w s
-- 
2011-05-19T00:26:42Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-05-19/china-to-curb-three-gorges-dam-environmntal-impact-xinhua-news-reports.html
China will take steps to curb
environmental deterioration in the Three Gorges Dam project
areas by 2020, Xinhua News Agency reported, citing a State
Council meeting presided over by Premier  Wen Jiabao .  The government will target the middle and lower reaches of
the  Yangtze River  to improve long-term geological disaster
prevention, Xinhua said, citing a State Council statement.  Efforts to preserve the ecology and biological diversity of
the area will also be increased, Xinhua said.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Gregory Turk at 
 gturk2@bloomberg.net  